message: "If you reference or build on VaultProof Agent Guard, please cite it as below."
title: "VaultProof Agent Guard — Pre-execution wallet guard for AI agents (alpha)"
abstract: >-
  VaultProof Agent Guard is a non-custodial, pre-execution wallet guard for AI
  agents. It evaluates proposed blockchain transactions (spend caps, allowlists,
  drain vectors, parameter integrity) and returns ALLOW / HOLD / DENY before
  anything signs. Built on the ExecutionProof gate and RF-100 governance standard.
  This is an experimental alpha reference implementation with reproducible tests.
  Not audited; not for production funds.
type: software
